Bhatnagar, Director & Founder Principal, Manav Sthali School at an award ceremony held at India International Centre, Max Mueller Marg, Delhi on Saturday, 6th July 2019 by Mrs Meenakshi Lekhi, Hon’ble Member of Parliament. The institution was awarded for making Education as the means for Nation building and for creating a New World Order with contribution from enlightened Indian minds', 'Manav Sthali School secured second position for making 6581 learners literate under the Delhi Schools Literacy Project (DSLP) and was awarded at the Springdales School, Dhaula Kuan on 26th April 201']
